Given a string consisting of digits (e.g., "50552"), find the largest 2-digit number that appears as a consecutive fragment in the string.

public int solution(String s) {
int max=0;

for(int i=0;i<s.length();i++){
// extract 2 consecutive characters
String fragment= s.substring(i,i+2);
//convert to int
int value=Integer.parse(fragment);

if(value>max){
max=value;
}
}
return max;
}
